r, it is likely that many previous records of \"H. cineraceus\" from Borneo refer to this species. Most records of the species are from lowland evergreen rainforest, though one record from Sabah was at 1800m. The roosting sites for this new species are currently unknown. Future research with a combination of data such as genetics, echolocation and morphology would be necessary to further determine the species geographic distribution in Southeast Asia.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Wongwaiyut, Phutita", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Karapan, Sunate", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Saekong, Puchit", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Francis, Charles M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guill\u00e9n-Servent, Antonio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Senawi, Juliana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Khan, Faisal Ali Anwarali", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bates, Paul J. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jantarit, Sopark", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Soisook, Pipat", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/a9a30b1905efb9f1f8897571c97e8d02", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9537e61cd8e9687d79891577100dd77b4b5ffa4b996572ba7f6e61d5bcfc3386", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/FRCJV3GY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/FRCJV3GY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/53fb1cebf5c945fe4ed2984b5b9361a2!/b280649-283219", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "cus